Available via `tw-animate-css` package:
- `animate-accordion-up`, `animate-accordion-down`
- `animate-in`, `animate-out`
- `fade-in-0`, `fade-out-0`
- `zoom-in-95`, `zoom-out-95`
- `slide-in-from-top-2`, `slide-in-from-bottom-2`, etc.

